    "note_tweet": {
      "entities": {},
      "text": "Unfortunately… there are so many people in this world exactly like this: they always try to prove themselves “right” by insulting and belittling others (of course that doesn’t actually make them right, but they think it does). All they care about is “winning,” with zero capacity for independent thought. Worse, they’re complete opportunists — they side with whichever view seems to be winning at the moment, switch camps instantly, and will never, ever admit they were wrong. Honestly, it really disgusts me to share the same species with them.\n\n遗憾的是……世界上有许多人就是这样的，他们总是靠辱骂贬低他人来凸显自己的正确（事实当然并非如此，但他们自以为是这样），脑子里只想着怎么「赢」，根本没有独立思考。而且墙头草，哪种观点赢面大他们跟哪边，随时转换阵营、永远不会承认错误。说真的我很不爽自己和他们同为人类。"
    },
